{
  "id": "69f5e18eb3cd1312380ea7f2",
  "title": "不審なお金の流れは流出元よりも寧ろ流入先のほうが気になる",
  "created": 1777721743,
  "updated": 1777721830,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69f5e18eb3cd1312380ea7f2",
      "text": "不審なお金の流れは流出元よりも寧ろ流入先のほうが気になる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777721743,
      "updated": 1777721769
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5e18e0000000000a3e7dc",
      "text": "from [2026/04/25]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777721743,
      "updated": 1777721743
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5e18e0000000000a3e7dd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777721743,
      "updated": 1777721760
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5e18e0000000000a3e7de",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777721743,
      "updated": 1777721743
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5e18e0000000000a3e7df",
      "text": " [不審なお金の流れ]は流出元よりも寧ろ流入先のほうが気になる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777721743,
      "updated": 1777721792
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5e18e0000000000a3e7e0",
      "text": " \t誰が受け取っているんだろう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777721743,
      "updated": 1777721743
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5e18e0000000000a3e7e1",
      "text": " \t流出元は分かりやすい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777721743,
      "updated": 1777721743
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5e18e0000000000a3e7e2",
      "text": " \t\t被害届を出す、報告をする",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777721743,
      "updated": 1777721743
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5e18e0000000000a3e7e3",
      "text": " \t流入先は分かりづらい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777721743,
      "updated": 1777721802
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5e18e0000000000a3e7e4",
      "text": " \t\t言わない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777721743,
      "updated": 1777721743
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5e18e0000000000a3e7e5",
      "text": " \t仮に[社会的組織]から[反社会的組織]に流出したとしたら、流入先はそりゃあ言わないだろう。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777721743,
      "updated": 1777721783
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5e18e0000000000a3e7e6",
      "text": " \t\t流出元は社会的組織なので[説明責任]を問われる。非対称。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777721743,
      "updated": 1777721814
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5e18e0000000000a3e7e7",
      "text": "\t\t[解明のための労力]が凄そう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777721743,
      "updated": 1777721830
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5e18e0000000000a3e7e8",
      "text": "\t\tだからといって流出被害元にさらなる[社会的圧力]がかかるのも[理不尽]な話",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777721743,
      "updated": 1777721825
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5e18e0000000000a3e7e9",
      "text": "\t\t\t[多大なるご心配をおかけし]……。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777721743,
      "updated": 1777721818
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5e18e0000000000a3e7ea",
      "text": "\t\t\t[公正世界仮説]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777721743,
      "updated": 1777721743
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5e18e0000000000a3e7eb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777721743,
      "updated": 1777721743
    }
  ]
}